Citation: Hody, J.W. & Kays, R. (in review) Mapping the expansion of coyotes (Canis latrans) across North and Central America.
dataIdInfo.idPurp:
This shapefile depicts the approximate geographic range of coyotes (Canis latrans) across North and Central America in each decade from 1900-2016. The methods used to produce this figure are reported in Hody & Kays (in review). File last updated: 21-July-2017. This file and derivations thereof may be used for non-commercial purposes only.
When using this dataset, please cite the original article: Hody, J.W. & Kays, R. (in review) Mapping the expansion of coyotes (Canis latrans) across North and Central America.
